name: HONK
description: If you are a video game lover, you have probably heard of the game that has become a phenomenon in the world "The Anonymous Goose Game - The famous goose with the desire to one day become the boss. We hope Honk BSC will create a new phenomenon just like the game did. If You Missed Honk Sol - Don't Miss Honk BSC. Honk has come to the BSC network and will create magic with this network of millions of users. What do you expect Honk to bring when appearing on BSC? We believe that Honk will make a difference with many of its big plans. With an experienced implementation team, many big partners, famous KOLs in the market, multinational coverage plan,... Honk will reach special milestones. When joining the Honk community, you will bring yourself many interesting experiences, interact and connect with many people with the same investment interests, experience together and bring profits together.
